layoutDesc.layout: Written in 14 and 17 long lines (dimensions of written space: 69 x 48 mm and 72 x 28 mm); frame rules in ink; prickings in outer margin.

decoDesc.decoNote: Blue, red, green and gold border on leaf 13r; Gold leaf, red and blue initials with some border on leaves 79r, 99r and 119r; Blue with red flourish initials on leaves 27r, 41r, 47r, 52r, 57r, 63r, 73r, 84v, 87r, 89r, 91r, 93r, 96v; Red and blue initials throughout.
Inside front coverBookplate, The Folger Shakespeare Library

binding.p: Bound in leather with gold tooling on spine; marbled paper pastedowns under endleaves. Spine title: Cultus sanctor.
